Name: Engine Evolution 2020
About the game: SUPPORT WILL END SOON Support for EngineEvolution 2020 will end soon, download 2021 instead: / Your progress WILL NOT be lost! :) About the game Engine Evolution is a multiplayer racing game that uses similar principles as World of Tanks - with each race, against 11 other players, you gain experience and credits, for which you can buy various upgrades for your bike, or unlock the next bike. You start with machines of 1906, can you get to the very top and ride on modern technology? Main features - Multiplayer PvP races - Simplified racing life simulator - 20 real historic vehicles - Real circuits - Varied customization - Matchmaking - Realistic graphics - Cloud save - Leaderboards - Daily missions About Me Developed mainly by one person! Engine Evolution began in 2016 as a Racing 300. First, the Hořice Circuit was created, then the game expanded with AI and other circuits. I worked on the game during my studies at MFF UK. In the end, I decided to try to make an MMO game in one and the result is Engine Evolution.
